{"TopicId":198210,"ForumId":32,"TopicTitle":"Lights for Island and Dessert airfields","CreatedByName":"Sppion1","CreatedById":198924,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-11-19T19:34:56Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Sppion1","CreatedById":198924,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-11-19T19:34:56Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHi everybody,\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIs there a way (probably a mod ?) to have dessert anr island airfields illuminated at night like \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Space Center\u0022\u003Eksc\u003C/abbr\u003E\u0027s runway ? Could be pretty usefull to land at night...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThanks \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/kerbal-forum-uploads/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHappy launches and landings \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/kerbal-forum-uploads/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Caerfinon","CreatedById":207619,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-11-19T19:40:57Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nKerbal-Konstructs lets you create bases with those types of effects\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedauthorid=\u0022167349\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed7135645614\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/151818-181-kerbal-konstructs-18115-15dec2019/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022 style=\u0022height:197px;max-width:502px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nKerbin Side Remastered includes several additional bases\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedauthorid=\u002262742\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed6768507457\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/174336-kerbin-side-remastered-101-173/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022 style=\u0022height:197px;max-width:502px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Sppion1","CreatedById":198924,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-11-19T19:51:21Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThanks, I\u0027ll give it a shot, although I thought it would be easier than adding that much building. Maybe with Kerbal Konstruct I could just add light to existing ones ? Or I\u0027ll try KerbinSide, don\u0027t know yet.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThanks anyway \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/kerbal-forum-uploads/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"fourfa","CreatedById":151713,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-11-19T22:15:52Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nComing soon in stock KSP \u00A0update 1.11:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedauthorid=\u0022196576\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed4765364441\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/197799-ksp-loadingpreview-new-lights/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022 style=\u0022height:375px;max-width:502px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWould be a fun mission to go line the runway with guide lights\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Caerfinon","CreatedById":207619,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-11-19T22:34:01Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223883746\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022198210\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221605824152\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022151713\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022fourfa\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n17 minutes ago, fourfa said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWould be a fun mission to go line the runway with guide lights\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAs long as we could anchor them to the ground, otherwise they will \u0022roam\u0022.\u00A0 But that could be fun too \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/kerbal-forum-uploads/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Stone Blue","CreatedById":77721,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-11-19T22:42:27Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/198924-sppion1/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022198924\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/198924-sppion1/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Sppion1\u003C/a\u003E if you install KerbalKonstructs, you can install an update of the old \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Space Center\u0022\u003E\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Space Center\u0022\u003EKSC\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003C/abbr\u003E Floodlight mod, of the light tower from the old Kosmodrome mod, here:\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022https://github.com/StoneBlue/KSC-Floodlights/releases\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://github.com/StoneBlue/\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Space Center\u0022\u003E\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Space Center\u0022\u003EKSC\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003C/abbr\u003E-Floodlights/releases\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIts *only* the light tower, not anything else in Kosmodrome.\u003Cbr\u003E\nJust be aware, if you run GPP, you have to delete the KSCFloodlight folder, packaged *deep* in the GPP folder.\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nImage provided by \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/114974-shoe7ess/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022114974\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/114974-shoe7ess/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@shoe7ess\u003C/a\u003E in a post from the \u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/122175-105-ksc-floodlight-24022016/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003Eoriginal \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Space Center\u0022\u003EKSC\u003C/abbr\u003E Floodlight thread\u003C/a\u003E:\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u002277XBeM7.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u0022166.67\u0022 height=\u0022681\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/77XBeM7.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222020-11-19T22:44:51Z\u0022 title=\u002211/19/2020 10:44  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00223 yr\u0022\u003ENovember 19, 2020\u003C/time\u003E by Stone Blue\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Corona688","CreatedById":2511,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-11-20T15:00:50Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThose dessert airfields sound delicious.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Sppion1","CreatedById":198924,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-11-20T15:07:56Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThanks all for your help \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/kerbal-forum-uploads/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSo I get what I wanted with Kerbal Konstruct, just searched for \u0022how to use kerbal konstruct\u0022, and found a \u0022dessert runway light\u0022 part that I put on the dessert runwau and on the island.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHappy launches and happy landings to everyone !\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nPS : \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/2511-corona688/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u00222511\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/2511-corona688/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Corona688\u003C/a\u003EThat\u0027s the name in game, just look at it \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/kerbal-forum-uploads/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Vanamonde","CreatedById":27914,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-11-20T22:48:35Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou can just make some light sources as craft and park them around the runways. That\u0027s what I do sometimes.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}